cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with computer-aided disease classification using image features and graph networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques for feature learning, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new network architecture, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of graph networks and signal processing techniques could also suggest cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
